2.00	Poule_d'Essai_des_Poulains	Poule d'Essai des Poulains	The Poule d'Essai des Poulains, sometimes referred to as the French 2,000 Guineas, is a Group 1 flat horse race in France open to three-year-old thoroughbred colts. It is run at Longchamp over a distance of 1,600 metres (about 1 mile), and it is scheduled to take place each year in May.	
